data.description:
Lots of updates in this Massillon home! 4-bedroom 2-full bath raised ranch located on a beautiful corner lot in Mayflower Village close to schools and shopping!
The main level of the home has an inviting living room that opens up to the eat-in kitchen with custom island and pantry, 3 bedrooms, and updated full bath. Original hardwood floors, reset lighting, replacement windows, newer interior doors and new trim throughout the home! Head to the finished lower level to find the primary bedroom with ensuite, recreation room, large mudroom and laundry room. The garage is perfect for a Man Cave or park your car there! Fully fenced-in yard/patio area with large shed and tetherball system offers a nice private retreat or swing on the tire swing in the side yard! This home is ready for new owners to make it their own! Seller's are also offering a one-year home warranty to the next owners!
